title: FAA projects continuing growth in commercial space transportation
description:
The Federal Aviation Administration office that regulates commercial spaceflight expects continued growth in launches, despite industry concerns about whether the office can keep pace.

The post FAA projects continuing growth in commercial space transportation appeared first on SpaceNews.
